{"id": 7859, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2020", "session": "20N", "subtopic": "8-1-theories-of-acids-and-bases", "title": "20N.1.SL.TZ0.20", "topic_id": "8", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>Which of these acids has the weakest conjugate base?</p>\n<p>A.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>HCl</mi></math></p>\n<p>B.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>CH</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mi>COOH</mi></math></p>\n<p>C.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>NH</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mi>Cl</mi></math></p>\n<p>D.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mn>6</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">H</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><mi>COOH</mi></math></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>More than 59% of the candidates understood that strong acids have weak conjugate bases.</p>\n</div>"}